Use this tutorial:
http://ddokkddokk.tistory.com/5

if you run a 64 bit version of Linux export the following variables:
# export CFLAGS=”−fPIC ”
# export CPPFLAGS=$CFLAGS
# export CXXFLAGS=$CFLAGS

Just to play safe clear the above defined variables:
# export CFLAGS=
# export CPPFLAGS=
# export CXXFLAGS=

For libpng, run:
sudo apt-get install libpng-dev
https://askubuntu.com/questions/508934/how-to-install-libpng-and-zlib
